<br>
He quit Everquest a while ago, and abandoned his Bard and leveled a wizard to the mid 50's. The day after he cancelled his account he took his wizard to Lesser Faydark, and asked the group hunting the brownines if he could take a few. he explained his early days of his bard, and they readily agreed.<br>
