<br>
Well, I kind of feel bad bugging people over stupid stuff...like freaking out over loosing my body (and not even having the right zone) at lvl 10.  Although I did ask for help with the body thing.  The girl that helped me was really nice too.  Especially since I had to SHOUT.  I know that THAT in itself annoys people, but when I got to BB (where I THOUGH that my original body was) I could not remember the /tell, /group, /shout, /occ, whatever command to talk to people just in my ZONE.  So I &quot;politely&quot; shouted: <br>
<br>
&quot;If anyone in BB sees my body, it is right on a path, can you please send me the /loc of it, sorry to shout, but I still don't know how to use this chat thing right.&quot;<br>
<br>
SO anyway, this girl told me to do /corpse and it said I had no body in that zone.  Once I got to LF (she said I had to be there if I entered from GF and was not in BB), it DID say my body was there (just too far away to summon).  She taught me how to make a BLANK button into a corpse key though (but I messed that up too, just put the text ON the button but no command in).  However she was REALLY patient and walked me through all of it until I FINALLY got it.  Once I totally understood what she was telling me...to go invisible, then stand right ON my body, then RUN like crazy to the zone line, pushing the /corpse button ALL the time...I FINALLY got them all to the zone line and looted them.  Man, I had a HUGE pile o' bodies.<br>
<br>
Anyway...sometimes I don't know if I should trust people though either if I don't KNOW them.  SHE was great and SO was the guy that ported me to the moon.  BUT...I was really nervous of HIM at FIRST.  <br>
<br>
See, I met him becuase when I was standing in the spires waiting to take off to the moon...he was standing there too.  I am not sure what class he was (can't remember and it wasn't a normal class either, one of the name changes) but I did the &quot;who&quot; thing and found his name and he was lvl 57 (or 53?) so I figured that he knew WHERE to stand and that if I stood near him, that I would be in the right place.  Well, I did say Hail to him when I FIRST started waiting for the moon (and it was just the two of us there), but he ignored me.  So I just kept standing there, keeping quite, waiting for the moon thing to happen.  <br>
<br>
THEN, after the first two groups disappear (and I kept seeing the countdown start over YET AGAIN) I finally asked him IF I was in the right place...I told him that I DID have my stone from the lady, etc.  I guess he wasn't going in the spires to the moon, but just hanging out doing whatever.  That is when he offered to port me there (and I flew to Kelethin over and over, etc.)<br>
<br>
BUT...see in the mean time (before I stated talking to him, but AFTER he ignored me the first time)...ALL of these people kept coming up to him asking him for money and eqipment and buffs, etc.   Anyway at one point he had three of them all talking at once and SWARMING around him.  They were ALL THREE jumping UP and DOWN too, like a bunch of rabbits.  I could tell that he was getting annoyed but I was just standing there waiting on the moon TRYING to mind my own business.  But I was bored since I had been standing there for like 40 minutes at that point, so even though he ignored me before, I sent him a tell and said &quot;LOL, looks like you have aquired a coterie.&quot;  So he tells me &quot;If I wouldn't get in trouble I would port them all to SkyFire.&quot;  Well, when I looked that up on my map, I saw that it was in Kunark (where someone told me not to go until I was lvl 30+, which is why LAST weekend I jumped off the flat boat and fell in the water when I got on the WRONG boat from the port in BB to Freeport).  <br>
<br>
SO...when he tried to port me to the moon and I FLEW/BOUNCED to Kelithen (Kelithin?)  and saw HIM no where around, I knew that it *looked* like Kelethin and NOT like I *thought* the moon would look like...but I wasn't sure where I was at first.  I didn't see those lift ramps, just tree house lights above.  THEN after we tried tried THREE times and I kept BOUNCING to Kelethin, he was like, &quot;well...let's see if I can port you somewhere ELSE&quot;.  Now THAT worked (we went to some place that I had never seen, but only for a second, then he told me to gate back...he bound me at the Spires) and he would meet me there after I REGISTERED the expansion.  <br>
<br>
I kept telling him that if had other stuff to do that I could try and figure it out on my own.  But after he told me earlier that he wished he could port those people to SkyFire, I was kind of nervous about going anywhere with him.  ESPECIALLY after I kept bouncing to Kelethin (I though that maybe it was annoying him by bouncing).  In reality, I think he probably just wanted to make sure his port thing was working (which is why he ported me somewhere else for a minute).  But I was getting really scared that he might just drop me off somewhere to get eaten.  He didn't though, he was really nice.  But I WAS kind of scared of him for a while.  I don't know WTF I would do if someone ported me to somewhere REALLY dangerous.  I guess I would be stuck there for good.   <p><center><img src="http://www.boomspeed.com/apothokeri/DraccaSig.gif"><br><br><b><font face="garamond" size=3><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=543802">My Magelo Profile</a></center><font size=0 font face=garamond font color=black></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=draccaviir>Dracca Viir</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.boomspeed.com/apothokeri/staricon.jpg" BORDER=0> at: 1/19/03 3:20:38 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=draccaviir>Dracca Viir</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.boomspeed.com/apothokeri/staricon.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 168<br> <font color=#333333>(1/19/03 3:15:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26.topic&index=2