<br>
It helps to have a hotkey with the following on it--<br>
<br>
/corpse<br>
<br>
This &quot;drags&quot; your corpse (or another persons who has used the /consent command).<br>
<br>
In many cases, the best thing you can do is go INVIS to go get your corpse.  Target body, and then start hitting the /corpse hotkey as you run to a place of safety and drag the corpse along.  Then you can loot it and be back on your way.<br>
<br>
Now there are some places that INVIS won't help.  But for now, you should be ok for quite a few levels.  Until you go to Unrest or some other place <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
